               <msContents>
                  <summary>I) Introduction
 - Maqdǝma Wangel “Introduction to the Gospels”
                     (fols. 1ra-9rb)
 - Letter of Eusebius to Carpianus (fols. 9rb-9va)
 -
                     The "Synopsis of Classes" (fols. 9va-10ra)
 - Canon tables (fols.
                     10ra-14vb)
 II) Gospel of Matthew (fols. 17ra-68rb)
 - Bǝsrāta Mātewos
                     “Gospel of Matthew” (fols.17ra-68rb) 
 - Postscript (fol. 68rb)
 III)
                     Gospel of Mark (fols. 69ra-98rb)
 - Bǝsrāta Mārqos “Gospel of Mark” (fols.
                     69ra-98rb)
 - Postscript (fol. 98rb)
 IV) Gospel of Luke
                     (fols.99ra-151rb)
 - Bǝsrāta Luqās “Gospel of Luke” (fols. 99ra-151ra)
                     - Postscript (fol. 151ra)
 - List of the “tituli” for the Gospel of Luke –
                     19 titles (fol.151rb)
 V) Gospel of John (fols. 152ra-196va)
 - Bǝsrāta
                     Yoḥannǝs “Gospel of John” (fols. 152ra-196va)
 - Postscript (fol.
                     196va)
 - List of the “tituli” for the Gospel of John – 19 titles (fol.
                     196vb)
 
 Additiones.</summary>
